    </section>

    {/* Content Section */}
    <section class="section-padding">
      <div class="section-container max-w-4xl mx-auto space-y-8">

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-foreground">
          Trusted Hip Replacement Surgeon in Manikonda
        </h2>
        <p class="text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">
          Chronic hip pain can severely limit mobility and quality of life. At
