          Manikonda, patients receive comprehensive evaluation and modern hip
          replacement treatment tailored to their needs.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-foreground">
          When Is Hip Replacement Recommended?
        </h2>
        <ul class="space-y-3 text-muted-foreground">
          <li class="flex gap-2">
            <CheckCircle2 class="w-5 h-5 text-primary" />
            Severe hip arthritis not responding to medication
          </li>
          <li class="flex gap-2">
            <CheckCircle2 class="w-5 h-5 text-primary" />
            Persistent hip pain affecting daily activities
          </li>
          <li class="flex gap-2">
            <CheckCircle2 class="w-5 h-5 text-primary" />
            Hip joint damage due to injury or degeneration
          </li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-foreground">
          Advanced Total Hip Replacement in Hyderabad
        </h2>
        <p class="text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">
          Using modern surgical techniques and high-quality implants, Dr. Karthik
          Manchala performs total hip replacement to relieve pain and restore
          movement. The goal is faster recovery, reduced discomfort, and long-term
          joint function.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-foreground">
          Why Choose Dr. Karthik Manchala for Hip Replacement?
        </h2>
        <p class="text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">
          As a leading orthopaedic surgeon in Manikonda, Dr. Karthik Manchala
          offers patient-focused care, thorough diagnosis, and post-operative
          rehabilitation guidance. Patients from Alkapur Township, Puppalaguda,
          Narsingi, and nearby Hyderabad areas trust his expertise in hip
          replacement surgery.
        </p>

      </div>
    </section>

    {/* Booking Form */}
    <BookingForm client:load />

    <Footer client:load />
    <FloatingButtons client:load />
  </div>
</Layout>
